3. ROYALTY-BASED LICENSING (Unreal Engine Model)
   Revenue-based tiers for companies using Δₛ³ in production:
   
   Tier 1 - Free (Non-Commercial / Startups < 1M€ revenue/year)
     - Cost: FREE
     - Scope: Academic, open-source, indie developers, personal projects
     - Obligation: "Powered by Δₛ³" credit
   
   Tier 2 - Small Business (1M€ - 10M€ revenue/year)
     - Royalties: 2% of revenue generated by Δₛ³-powered features
     - OR Flat license: 5,000€/year
     - Support: Email + GitHub Issues
   
   Tier 3 - Enterprise (> 10M€ revenue/year)
     - Royalties: 5% of revenue generated by Δₛ³-powered features
     - OR Flat license: 50,000€/year
     - Support: SLA, priority issues, custom features
   
   Note: "Revenue generated by Δₛ³-powered features" means revenue
   directly attributable to products/services that use the Licensed Work
   as a core component (e.g., search API, chatbot service, RAG system).

4. REVENUE REPORTING
